text: Andrea Arnaboldi and Antonio Šančić were the defending champions but only Šančić chose to defend his title, partnering Marin Draganja. Šančić lost in the first round to Julian Knowle and Jonathan Marray. Evgeny Donskoy and Mikhail Elgin won the title after defeating Knowle and Marray 6–4, 3–6, [11–9] in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Open de Rennes - Doubles Category:Open de Rennes
title: 2017 Open de Rennes – Doubles
